"Block every change; reads only." = "すべての変更をブロックし、読み取りのみ許可します。";
"Applies to the kube API servers from this profile's kubeconfigs (e.g. `kubectl delete` fails cleanly)." = "このプロファイルの kubeconfig にある kube API サーバーに適用されます（例: `kubectl delete` は正常に失敗します）。";
"All *.amazonaws.com APIs; classified by action name (Delete*/Terminate* = destructive, Get*/List*/Describe* = read)." = "すべての *.amazonaws.com API。アクション名で分類されます（Delete*/Terminate* = 破壊的、Get*/List*/Describe* = 読み取り）。";
"api.digitalocean.com — DELETE = destructive." = "api.digitalocean.com — DELETE = 破壊的。";
"Registries you've added under Credentials — pull = read, push = write, delete = destructive." = "「資格情報」で追加したレジストリ — pull = 読み取り、push = 書き込み、delete = 破壊的。";
"github.com REST API + git over HTTPS; read-only also blocks `git push`." = "github.com REST API と HTTPS 経由の git。読み取り専用では `git push` もブロックされます。";
"gitlab.com REST API + git over HTTPS." = "gitlab.com REST API と HTTPS 経由の git。";
